caption.text:
july 12th 2017. someday i'll be looking back on my life at the memories and this is going to be one of them.
.
i entered @mrmslspr expecting it to be just like any other journey. only later did i realize that there is so much more to the experience than meets the eye. it was a true learning process, in which we are encouraged to grow.
.
three months in and it was never easy. but when you have faith and you got your family, there is no obstacle too great to overcome.
.
all in all, here goes my small token of gratitude. thank you @mrmslspr and @lsprjakarta for the experience, for placing your trust and confidence in me. thank you seniors, alumnis, and mentors. you left us such big shoes to fill. to 2017, buckle up and get ready for another journey. thank you for the memory. xx
